locality: Plateau du Tango. Pine plantation with patches of native vegetation, especially in gullies.
Province du Nord. Mt. Panié, above Haut Coulna, on SW forested slopes.

Upper Tchamba River valley, W of Wâo Uni, along new logging road toward Tiapayi. Humid forest along road. Non-ultramafic substrate. Collected with J. Munzinger, M. Schlessman, L. Vary, A. Mouly & T. Le Borgne.
